{"tid":1784191,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"兩名中國外交官擅闖軍事基地 被美國驅逐出境","createTime":"2019-12-15T13:18:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T16:09:18.000Z","uid":41404,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"3f37e1ea1e3011e3c9aa051169f3529f2fbc38d6","tid":1784191,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T13:18:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2019/12/15/world/asia/us-china-spies.html?smid=nytcore-ios-share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2019%2F12%2F15%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fus-china-spies.html%3Fsmid%3Dnytcore-ios-share&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hvilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=99288070\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/2019/12/15/world/asia/us-china-spies.html?smid=nytcore-ios-share</a>"},{"pid":"4fa519bba0fcd1deae45f69c2ef335a4f220f07d","tid":1784191,"uid":41404,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T13:19:00.000Z","msg":"WASHINGTON &mdash; The American government secretly expelled two Chinese Embassy officials this fall after they drove on to a sensitive military base in Virginia, according to people with knowledge of the episode. The expulsions appear to be the first of Chinese diplomats suspected of espionage in more than 30 years.<br />\n<br />\nAmerican officials believe at least one of the Chinese officials, who were with their wives, was an intelligence officer operating under diplomatic cover, said six people with knowledge of the expulsions. The group evaded military personnel pursuing them and stopped only after fire trucks blocked their path."},{"pid":"82b90f9d3ec46314b5eb6e7ec58d7ac64b36c972","tid":1784191,"uid":169079,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T13:19:07.000Z","msg":"間諜活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66ea7f5e7a56fa0b5bc4945e762d7c07472601f8","tid":1784191,"uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T13:19:36.000Z","msg":"The episode in September, which neither Washington nor Beijing announced, has intensified concerns in the Trump administration that China is expanding its spying efforts in the United States as the two nations are increasingly locked in a geopolitical and economic rivalry. American intelligence officials say China poses a greater espionage threat than any other country.<br />\n<br />\nIn recent months, Chinese officials with diplomatic passports have become bolder about showing up unannounced at research or government facilities, American officials said, with the infiltration of the military base only the most remarkable instance."},{"pid":"5be3a1f025538b0e1d7ffce58bfde30801a6fd70","tid":1784191,"uid":202524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T13:19:47.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借個位黎<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">德國戰線要人</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"976f40a52dd0b56fbdb0c719544e0ad9d70ca436","tid":1784191,"uid":110079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T13:21:16.000Z","msg":"推行動po<br />\n【重推-仲有冇火?】1231築人鏈 1月1日街上見！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1784122\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1784122</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a6c5f2aee6d050e5f87fa528fc7e82a4ea4048e6","tid":1784191,"uid":258687,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T13:21:41.000Z","msg":"開戰？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cebdceaec18708b4e0c0f32aec2ef15915ed60dc","tid":1784191,"uid":222970,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T13:21:54.000Z","msg":"直接開槍射殺啦屌 中國人咁兇狠點知佢哋係咪恐怖襲擊啊"},{"pid":"17c2152e884fb22500f385678e7c700dd26427eb","tid":1784191,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":